summary: This is an email exchange between two individuals, likely within the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York, regarding obtaining a copy of a document referred to as the 'Epstein Photo Book.' The email references the document's location in a specific production (the 18th production) within a shared case directory.
locations: One Saint Andrew's Plaza, New York, NY 10007
keyFacts: An email exchange dated September 29, 2021, concerns obtaining a copy of a document titled 'Epstein Photo Book'.
The requested document is identified as being part of the '18th production' dated July 28, 2021, in the case US v. Epstein.
The correspondence originates from or is directed to an Assistant United States Attorney at the Southern District of New York.
The document's file path suggests it is stored on a shared government network drive related to the Epstein case discovery.
